                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9149" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CPGN-0272</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1419 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“氢”尽全力：ESG理念下未势能源的价值创造之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Hydrogen&quot; Full Steam Ahead: The Path to Value Creation for FTXT Energy under the ESG Concept</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨忠海，刘金奇（通讯作者），毕鹏，李雪</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">哈尔滨工程大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">未势能源科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG；价值创造；公司治理；可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG ; Value growth;Corporate governance; Sustainability</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在可持续发展背景下，ESG可以帮助企业协调与环境、社会的关系，从而实现长久的价值创造，尤其对于从事新能源领域的企业来说更是如此。本案例为描述型案例，对未势能源在ESG理念下的价值创造之路进行了梳理，论述了ESG的概念及内涵，分析了未势能源为什么要在发展与治理中融入ESG理念，进一步探讨了未势能源开展ESG实践的具体措施以及所创造的价值，并研究了ESG赋能未势能源实现价值共创与价值共享的机理。案例表明，在长期主义的指导下，未势能源将ESG融入企业自身的发展布局，从而改变了未势能源的价值导向，并通过产品落地与技术研发实现了企业价值与利益相关者价值的和谐统一。通过本案例的学习，使学生能够了解ESG的重要作用，并对价值共创和价值共享等相关知识和理论进行深入学习。本案例对当前我国企业在高质量发展的要求下贯彻ESG理念、实现企业与社会的可持续发展具有一定的启发和借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the view of sustainable development, ESG can help enterprises to harmonize their relationship with the environment and society, so as to realize long-term value creation, especially for enterprises engaged in the field of new energy. This case is a descriptive case, which comprehends the path of value creation of FTXT Energy under the ESG concept, discusses the concept and connotation of ESG, analyzes why FTXT Energy has to implement the ESG concept in its development and governance, further discusses the specific measures and value created by FTXT Energy&#39;s implementation of ESG, and studies the mechanism by which ESG empowers FTXT Energy to realise the value co-creating and value-sharing. The case shows that under the guidance of long-termism, FTXT Energy integrates ESG into the enterprise&#39;s own development layout, thus changing FTXT Energy&#39;s value orientation, and realizing the harmonious unity of enterprise value and stakeholder value through product implementation and technology development. Through the study of this case, students are able to understand the important role of ESG and learn in-depth about the related knowledge and theories of value co-creation and value sharing. This case has a certain inspiration and reference significance for Chinese enterprises to implement the ESG concept and realize the sustainable development of enterprises and society under the requirement of high-quality development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司治理》、《商业伦理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG的概念与内涵；ESG体系及ESG治理；ESG与可持续发展；ESG与利益相关者；ESG与价值共创、价值共享</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
